Package: orthoVar
Title: A package for finding orthologous variants between species.
Version: 0.4.0
Author: Mustafa Samet Pir
Maintainer: Mustafa Samet Pir <mustafapir29@gmail.com>
Description: This package provides functions for generating genome-wide multiple sequence alignments (msa) and finding orthologous variants between species
